OL,3,CPatients left in hospital corridors
OL,4,Cfor 'dangerously long periods',
OL,5,Cexperts warn
OL,7,FNHS patients are being left in
OL,8,Fhospital corridors for "dangerously
OL,9,Flong periods" and missing timely
OL,10,Faccess to specialist care, health
OL,11,Fleaders have warned.
OL,13,FThe Society for Acute Medicine (SAM)
OL,14,Fsaid new data shows fewer than one in
OL,15,Ffive acutely unwell patients are
OL,16,Freceiving their first assessment in an
OL,17,Facute medical unit (AMU).
OL,19,FAMUs are short stay assessment and
OL,20,Fadmission units for patients who need
OL,21,Fspecialist assessment and/or opinion.
