OL,3,CPatients left in hospital corridors
OL,4,Cfor 'dangerously long periods',
OL,5,Cexperts warn
OL,7,FSAM past president Dr Tim Cooksley
OL,8,Fadded: "We have patients in corridors,
OL,9,Fnot just in our emergency departments
OL,10,Fbut in our acute medical units as
OL,11,Fwell, and our occupancy levels are too
OL,12,Fhigh.
OL,14,F"We still have over 1,000 patients a
OL,15,Fday in England alone waiting more than
OL,16,F12 hours in emergency departments, and
OL,17,Fmost of those are acute medical
OL,18,Fpatients waiting for a bed on an acute
OL,19,Fmedical unit.
